revisions.rev:
In [[real estate]], '''racial steering''' is the act of steering prospective homebuyers to [[neighborhood]]s which have residents of mostly their same [[racial]] background. It is extremely controversial, being a form of (sometimes well-intentioned{{fact}}) [[racial segregation]] and leading to the creation of [[ghetto]]s{{fact}}.

